<b>Errors:</b>
Rates are per second, averaged over a 60 second interval
Traffic percentages(%) are based on error/packet ratio
Input alarm thresholds (traffic%):  yellow={ifInErrTraf.thresh:yellow}%, red={ifInErrTraf.thresh:red}% 
Output alarm thresholds (traffic%): yellow={ifOutErrTraf.thresh:yellow}%, red={ifOutErrTraf.thresh:red}% 
